  "body": "The following would be introduced to the file-explorer to improve git integration:\r\n- [x] #2451\r\n- [ ] #3113\r\n- [ ] Push to version control (github)/sync changes button/icon\r\n- [x] #2679\r\n- [ ] commit button that links to dgit plugin\r\n- [x] #2678\r\n- [ ] Show version control info in status bar plugin (branch, remote, version control name)\r\n- [x] Remove duplicate entry of github settings (settings tab or dgit). Discuss suitable options.\r\n- [ ] https://github.com/ethereum/remix-project/issues/3473 Improve git repo initialisation from the FE\r\n- [ ] https://github.com/ethereum/remix-project/issues/3474 integrate git with git lab\r\n\r\nSupport for other version control can be added later on.",
